OL,5, After a burglar stole thousands of     
OL,6, pounds worth of power tools from her   
OL,7, home, in St Albans, in October, Sharon 
OL,8, Allen turned amateur detective.        
OL,10,FShe began going house to house, making 
OL,11,Fher own inquiries, and handed CCTV     
OL,12,Ffootage from her neighbours to police. 
OL,14,F"He's got a distinctive nose," Ms Allen
OL,15,Ftells BBC News, as she examines her own
OL,16,Fblack-and-white security-camera        
OL,17,Ffootage.                               
OL,19,F"I've given them the information and   
OL,20,FI'm hoping they've looked at the CCTV."
